                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ari</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> A<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/>relio <supplied reason="lost">A</supplied>nt<supplied reason="lost">oni</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>no <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>F</abbr><ex>elici</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> po<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan></supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Atellius <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Ser(gia)</supplied> <lb n="6"/>Chanus<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ius</supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">Pa</supplied>uli<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>u<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="8"/>IIvir <lb n="9"/>ex <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Interpunktion: Hederae und Punkte. (A): Maßabweichungen. (B): Z.1-3: [Au]/relio Ant[oni]/no Aug(usto) [p(ontifici) max(imo)] Z. 5: Atelliu[s]; Z. 6/7: [Pa]/ul[i]n[us]. Nach J. Alvar Z. 6 Anfang: CHANVS vielleicht eigenständiges Cognomen. Datierung nach J. Alvar 1. Drittel 3. Jh. Material: weißlicher Kalkstein.</p>
            </div>
